        "title": "<ul><li><em>Round</em></li></ul>",
        "description": "<p>The most classic and widely recognised shape.<br/></p><ul><li>Symmetrical and balanced</li><li>Designed for maximum light reflection</li><li>Timeless and versatile</li></ul><p>Round stones offer a sense of familiarity and refinement - an enduring choice that transcends trends.</p>",
        "colour_style": "dark",
        "button_1_text": "",
