        "title": "<p><em>Emerald</em></p>",
        "description": "<p>A rectangular shape with step-cut facets.<br/></p><ul><li>Clean lines and architectural form</li><li>Emphasis on clarity over sparkle</li><li>Understated and refined<br/></li></ul><p>Emerald cuts reveal the internal character of a stone, favouring depth and stillness over brilliance.</p>",
